df2 = data.frame(pseudotime=0:max(df$pseudotime),
                 Nfia=0, Nfib=0, Nfic=0)

    df2[i, j] = mean(df[df$pseudotime > df2$pseudotime[i] - 5. & df$pseudotime < df2$pseudotime[i] + 5., j])
